    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "siege_weapon",
        "text": "A steel-banded marble orb etched with magical runes is attached to the end of this sleek battering ram. The orb transforms the momentum of its crew into pure force energy that can hurl smaller objects out of the way. Because of its magical nature, the muscle of the individual crew members isn\u2019t a factor in how hard an arcane ram hits.",
